c: 7
v: 43
t: "Tuzokuraho ingorane ziri mubikiriza vyabo hanyuma imbere yabo habe haraca inzuzi, hanyuma bazovuga bati:- ihayagizwa ryose ryiza niryo rikwiriye Imana, kuko ariyo yaturongoye muri iyi migisha turimwo, kandi ntitwari kuba turi mu bantu barongotse turi twenyene iyo Imana itaturongora, intumwa z’Umuremyi wacu nibo bazanye ukuri kandi aribo bazobwirwa yuko iri ariryo Juru mwemerewe kubera ivyo mwahora mugira"